OL,6,FMillions of pounds will be spent
OL,7,Ftrying to improve poor water quality
OL,8,Fnear Pontypool, Dwr Cymru Welsh Water
OL,9,Fhas announced.
OL,11,FThe water company is investing nearly
OL,12,F#13 million on upgrading the storm
OL,13,Foverflow to stop items like rags, wet
OL,14,Fwipes and sanitary products getting
OL,15,Finto the river.
OL,17,FIt said the water in the Afon Lwyd and
OL,18,FRiver Usk will be improved as a result.
