OL,3,CMillions spent on green scheme to cut
OL,4,Csewage in river
OL,6,F115,525 discharges into local
OL,7,Fwaterways were counted across Wales in
OL,8,F2023, according to the River Trust.
OL,10,FThat equates to more than 50 spills
OL,11,Fper each overflow pipe on average,
OL,12,Fwith untreated sewage discharged for
OL,13,Fover a million hours across the nation
OL,14,Flast year.
OL,16,FWelsh Water said the money "will
OL,17,Fimprove the way the waste network
OL,18,Foperates within the New Inn area."
