OL,4,Csewage in river
OL,6,FThe company added: "This in turn will
OL,7,Fhelp boost the water quality in the
OL,8,FAfon Lwyd and the River Usk."
OL,10,FAerated reed beds and other underwater
OL,11,Fplants are being installed to treat
OL,12,Fthe storm water before it is released
OL,13,Fback into the environment, preventing
OL,14,Fsewage from entering the rivers.
OL,16,FThe water company said "nature-based
OL,17,Fsolutions" such as this could be the
OL,18,Fway forward.
