OL,3,CMillions spent on green scheme to cut
OL,4,Csewage in river
OL,6,FHe added: "The purpose of this is to
OL,7,Fsee whether we can actually treat that
OL,8,Fstorm water (coming from local houses)
OL,9,Fusing nature-based solutions so
OL,10,Fthere's no impact on the river and we
OL,11,Fprotect the river but actually use
OL,12,Fnature for doing that treatment."
OL,14,FIt is hoped the project, which is the
OL,15,Ffirst of its kind in Wales, can be
OL,16,Frolled out elsewhere.
