OL,6,FMr Wilson explained: "We'll be
OL,7,Fsampling what comes in and what comes
OL,8,Fout to make sure it is treating to the
OL,9,Fstandard that we want and then if it
OL,10,Fis successful, as we hope it will be,
OL,11,Fwe will start to see more of these
OL,12,Fgoing in Wales because the more nature-
OL,13,Fbased solutions we can use, the better
OL,14,Ffor carbon. The better for the
OL,15,Fenvironment."
OL,17,F"It's a pilot and we do want to roll
OL,18,Fout more of these," he added.
