OL,6,FThe challenge of keeping up with
OL,7,Fclimate change will require work from
OL,8,Fthe water company for decades to come,
OL,9,Faccording to Mr Wilson.
OL,11,FIt is a hard task to meet, especially
OL,12,Fwhen trying to balance the need for
OL,13,Fwork with the subsequent cost.
OL,15,FCampaigner Ric Cooper from volunteer
OL,16,Fgroup the Cleddau Project said: "Not
OL,17,Fone, we need hundreds of these reed
OL,18,Fbeds all over the place to help stop
OL,19,Fthis flow of raw sewage into the
OL,20,Friver."
