OL,6,FOn the question of whether costs for
OL,7,Fwork being carried out now and in the
OL,8,Fyears ahead will be passed onto
OL,9,Fcustomers, Mr Wilson said: "Bills are
OL,10,Fgoing to have to go up because we all
OL,11,Fwant better, cleaner rivers. What
OL,12,Fwe're trying to do at Welsh Water is
OL,13,Fstrike the right balance between
OL,14,Fmaking sure bills are still affordable
OL,15,Fbut also meet the challenge of
OL,16,Fimproving the environment as fast as
OL,17,Fwe possibly can."
