OL,6,FMr Wilson said: "Climate change is
OL,7,Faccelerating but we've got to try and
OL,8,Fmake sure that the amount of work that
OL,9,Fwe're doing is still affordable for
OL,10,Fcustomers. There's no other source of
OL,11,Fmoney for paying for this work other
OL,12,Fthan customer bills and what Welsh
OL,13,FWater borrows."
OL,15,FHe added: "We're trying to do this as
OL,16,Ffast as we can but at a rate that
OL,17,Fcustomers can still afford to pay
OL,18,Ftheir bills."
