OL,6,FThe plans will "likely" mean Welsh
OL,7,FWater customers paying about #40 extra
OL,8,Fa year.
OL,10,FA Welsh Government spokesperson said:
OL,11,F"Ensuring our water is of the highest
OL,12,Fquality is a vital part of making
OL,13,FWales a prosperous, happy and healthy
OL,14,Fplace to live and work, and plays a
OL,15,Fcentral role in our response to the
OL,16,Fnature and climate emergencies.
