OL,6,FThe spokesperson added: "We are
OL,7,Factively supporting the implementation
OL,8,Fof nature-based solutions through our
OL,9,FSAC Rivers Action Plan to address
OL,10,Friver pollution, recognising that
OL,11,Fthese approaches not only reduce
OL,12,Fpollution but also enhance
OL,13,Fbiodiversity and promote ecosystem
OL,14,Fresilience.
OL,16,F"We all have a shared interest in
OL,17,Fimproving our river health across
OL,18,FWales, and it is vital we continue to
OL,19,Ftake a collaborative approach with
OL,20,Fgovernment, regulators and all
OL,21,Frelevant sectors working together."
